verbose_text: The results of western blot analyses (XREF_FIG) demonstrated that salidroside significantly reduced the expression of cytochrome c (P < 0.05; XREF_FIG) and the ratio of Bax / Bcl-2 compared with the ox-LDL treatment group, while these roles were abolished by transfection with siSIRT1 (XREF_FIG).
